// an achievement of an existing type means adding an entry here - no engine change, no new branch.
//
// This seed is the SOURCE OF TRUTH. Mid-event you may edit a doc straight in the Firestore console
// (that is the whole point of definitions being data - there is no redeploy window), but fold any
// such change back into this file afterwards so the reviewed record stays accurate.
//
